{"tid":1153941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天水圍2x歲仔危站企跳 警趕至時墮樓傷重死亡","createTime":"2019-05-14T03:12:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-16T16:43:53.000Z","uid":184679,"like":59,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"8030ee79a44f24aac850c704fb900f839aa2a46c","tid":1153941,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T03:12:51.000Z","msg":"天水圍天瑞邨一名男子危站走廊欄河外企跳，男子其後墮樓，跌落平台重傷。救護員到場，證實男子已傷重死亡，警方正調查男子的尋死原因。<br />\n<br />\n事發於天瑞邨瑞財樓，今早8時，警方接到一名男子報案，指其女友的20多歲兄長奪門離家，危站在走廊欄河外，企圖跳樓。警方趕到上址，接獲大廈保安報案指男事主已墮下，跌落平台重傷。救護員到場，證實男子已傷重死亡。警方正調查男子的尋死原因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1499686/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1499686%2F&d=4exhEwVElvs0p929i6aHT%2BaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=47954c2c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1499686%2F&h=8e03e817\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1499686/</a>"},{"pid":"ac5d6ae269dcc41c8b081606a1d70b64fcb0b174","tid":1153941,"uid":46078,"like":167,"dislike":13,"score":154,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T03:15:42.000Z","msg":"睇標題以為係 警墮樓亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12ef73c42e4f0ce701f3c2f2266d9f3883603f37","tid":1153941,"uid":67500,"like":3,"dislike":15,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T03:17:08.000Z","msg":"渣GA"},{"pid":"2e35100918f86ed71db6fcd1fdd038115dbd29a8","tid":1153941,"uid":113626,"like":36,"dislike":3,"score":33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T03:17:53.000Z","msg":"連登所謂既贏家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"916cf11930d5fa40e5a1ef9d94cbf637c70fc79d","tid":1153941,"uid":127988,"like":8,"dislike":19,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T03:18:35.000Z","msg":"自殺成功， 可喜可賀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkg